The '''Rhyos''', also known as the '''Jimera''', is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is found in the second floor of [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]]. Rhyos is a [[Fire (Final Fantasy element)|fire]]-based monster and often uses [[Blaze (Final Fantasy)|Blaze]] and [[Stone Gas (Final Fantasy)|Stone Gas]] on the entire [[party]] who should have [[Fire (Final Fantasy element)|fire]] and [[Stone (Final Fantasy)|stone]]-elemental protection to avoid damage and petrification.

